  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Body of student recovered from Upper Kothmalai Reservoir",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The body of a schoolgirl was recovered from the Mel Kothmalai reservoir under Thalawakkala police division at around 3 pm today.",
        "Police inform Thalivaka that the dead body of a 19-year-old student named Muturatinam Zilogini from Melaku Senai Estate, Linthulai, was recovered from the West Gothamala reservoir.",
        "Relatives of the student said that she left home this morning saying she was going to a private class in Thalaiwakagi, but the student did not go to the private class. It is revealed from the initial stage of police investigations that she is a student who has failed in the high level examination to be held this year and is a high level student of a school in Linthulai area.",
        "Today around 2 o'clock in the afternoon, local residents informed the police that they saw a dead body floating in the Upper Kothumalai water reservoir, and the police recovered the body with the help of local residents.",
        "The Dalawake police are continuing to carry out investigations related to the incident and they are taking steps to take the dead body to the Nuwara Eliya District Hospital for post-mortem."
      ],
